    {
      "text": "The sequel to the dating sim that rocked the world (maybe) in 1992! Doukyuusei 2 is a 1995 classic erotic love adventure, a genre that is also referred to as \"dating simulations\". It has a new location and new protagonist. The aim of the game is the same as the original.",
